{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "jury-ai-bloco2-2026",
    "name": "Jury AI - API (Bloco 2)",
    "description": "# Jury AI - Documentação da API\n\n## Visão geral\n\nAPI REST do projeto **Jury AI** (Bootcamp Pythonando - Construção da base). Todas as requisições (exceto Cadastro, Login e Refresh) devem enviar o header **Authorization: Bearer &lt;access_token&gt;**.\n\n## Variáveis de ambiente\n\n| Variável | Descrição | Exemplo |\n|----------|------------|--------|\n| `base_url` | URL base da API | http://localhost:8000 |\n| `user_email` | E-mail do usuário de teste | teste@jury.ai |\n| `user_password` | Senha do usuário de teste | senha1234 |\n| `auth_token` | JWT access (preenchido após Login/Cadastro) | — |\n| `refresh_token` | JWT refresh (preenchido após Login/Cadastro) | — |\n| `cliente_id` | ID de um cliente (preenchido após List/Create) | 1 |\n\n## Módulos\n\n| Módulo | Prefixo | Descrição |\n|--------|---------|----------|\n| Auth | /api/auth/ | Cadastro, login, refresh, perfil |\n| Clientes | /api/clientes/ | CRUD de clientes |\n| Documentos | /api/documents/ | Placeholder (IA/RAG) |\n| Chat | /api/chat/ | Placeholder (Chat IA) |\n",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "if (pm.environment.get('auth_token')) {",
          "  pm.request.headers.upsert({ key: 'Authorization', value: 'Bearer ' + pm.environment.get('auth_token') });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Authentication",
      "description": "Endpoints de **Cadastro**, **Login**, **Refresh Token** e **Me** (perfil). Login e Cadastro retornam `access` e `refresh`; use `access` no header Authorization nas demais requisições.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Cadastro",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "description": "Obrigatório para body JSON"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{user_email}}\",\n  \"username\": \"teste\",\n  \"first_name\": \"Teste\",\n  \"last_name\": \"User\",\n  \"password\": \"{{user_password}}\",\n  \"password_confirm\": \"{{user_password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/cadastro/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "cadastro", ""]
            },
            "description": "## POST /api/auth/cadastro/\n\nCria um novo usuário e retorna tokens JWT.\n\n### Parâmetros do body (JSON)\n\n| Campo | Tipo | Obrigatório | Descrição |\n|-------|------|-------------|----------|\n| email | string | Sim | E-mail único (será usado no login) |\n| username | string | Sim | Nome de usuário |\n| first_name | string | Não | Nome |\n| last_name | string | Não | Sobrenome |\n| password | string | Sim | Mínimo 8 caracteres |\n| password_confirm | string | Sim | Deve ser igual a password |\n\n### Resposta de sucesso (201)\n\n- `user`: objeto com id, email, username, first_name, last_name\n- `access`: JWT access token\n- `refresh`: JWT refresh token\n\n### Erros\n\n- **400** — Validação: senhas não coincidem, e-mail já existe, campo obrigatório ausente."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Cadastro 201 ou 400 (email já existe)', function () { pm.expect([201, 400]).to.include(pm.response.code); });",
                  "var res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.access) { pm.environment.set('auth_token', res.access); }",
                  "if (res.refresh) { pm.environment.set('refresh_token', res.refresh); }",
                  "if (res.user && res.user.id) { pm.environment.set('user_id', res.user.id); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "✅ 201 - Usuário criado",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\"email\": \"novo@jury.ai\", \"username\": \"novo\", \"first_name\": \"Novo\", \"last_name\": \"User\", \"password\": \"senha1234\", \"password_confirm\": \"senha1234\"}"
                }
              },
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"user\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"email\": \"novo@jury.ai\",\n    \"username\": \"novo\",\n    \"first_name\": \"Novo\",\n    \"last_name\": \"User\"\n  },\n  \"refresh\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n  \"access\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "❌ 400 - E-mail já existe",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\"email\": \"existente@jury.ai\", \"username\": \"x\", \"password\": \"senha1234\", \"password_confirm\": \"senha1234\"}"
                }
              },
              "status": "Bad Request",
              "code": 400,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"email\": [\"user with this e-mail already exists.\"]\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "description": "Obrigatório"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{user_email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{user_password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/token/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "token", ""]
            },
            "description": "## POST /api/auth/token/\n\nAutentica e retorna tokens JWT. Use o **access** no header `Authorization: Bearer <access>` nas próximas requisições.\n\n### Parâmetros do body (JSON)\n\n| Campo | Tipo | Obrigatório | Descrição |\n|-------|------|-------------|----------|\n| email | string | Sim | E-mail do usuário |\n| password | string | Sim | Senha |\n\n### Resposta de sucesso (200)\n\n- `access`: JWT access token\n- `refresh`: JWT refresh token\n- `user`: objeto com id, email, username, first_name, last_name\n\n### Erros\n\n- **400** — E-mail ou senha inválidos (`non_field_errors`)."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.access) { pm.environment.set('auth_token', res.access); }",
                  "if (res.refresh) { pm.environment.set('refresh_token', res.refresh); }",
                  "if (res.user && res.user.id) { pm.environment.set('user_id', res.user.id); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "✅ 200 - Login OK",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\"email\": \"teste@jury.ai\", \"password\": \"senha1234\"}"
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"access\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n  \"refresh\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n  \"user\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"email\": \"teste@jury.ai\",\n    \"username\": \"teste\",\n    \"first_name\": \"Teste\",\n    \"last_name\": \"User\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "❌ 400 - E-mail ou senha inválidos",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\"email\": \"errado@jury.ai\", \"password\": \"errada\"}"
                }
              },
              "status": "Unauthorized",
              "code": 401,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"detail\": \"E-mail ou senha inválidos.\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/token/refresh/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "token", "refresh", ""]
            },
            "description": "## POST /api/auth/token/refresh/\n\nRenova o **access token** usando o **refresh token**. Não requer Authorization.\n\n### Parâmetros do body (JSON)\n\n| Campo | Tipo | Obrigatório | Descrição |\n|-------|------|-------------|----------|\n| refresh | string | Sim | Refresh token JWT obtido no Login/Cadastro |\n\n### Resposta de sucesso (200)\n\n- `access`: novo JWT access token\n\n### Erros\n\n- **401** — Refresh token inválido ou expirado."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.access) { pm.environment.set('auth_token', res.access); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "✅ 200 - Novo access",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\"refresh\": \"<refresh_token>\"}"
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"access\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Me (perfil)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/me/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "me", ""]
            },
            "description": "## GET /api/auth/me/\n\nRetorna os dados do usuário autenticado. **Requer** header `Authorization: Bearer <access_token>`.\n\n### Resposta de sucesso (200)\n\nObjeto com: `id`, `email`, `username`, `first_name`, `last_name`.\n\n### Erros\n\n- **401** — Token ausente ou inválido."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.expect(res).to.have.property('email');",
                  "pm.expect(res).to.have.property('id');"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "✅ 200 - Perfil",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer <access_token>" }
                ]
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"email\": \"teste@jury.ai\",\n  \"username\": \"teste\",\n  \"first_name\": \"Teste\",\n  \"last_name\": \"User\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Clientes",
      "description": "CRUD de **Clientes**. Todas as requisições exigem autenticação. Cada usuário vê apenas seus próprios clientes.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Clientes",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/clientes/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "clientes", ""]
            },
            "description": "## GET /api/clientes/\n\nLista todos os clientes do usuário logado.\n\n### Headers\n\n- **Authorization**: Bearer &lt;access_token&gt; (obrigatório)\n\n### Resposta de sucesso (200)\n\nArray de objetos cliente, cada um com: `id`, `nome`, `email`, `telefone`, `cpf_cnpj`, `observacoes`, `criado_em`, `atualizado_em`.\n\n### Erros\n\n- **401** — Não autenticado."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.expect(res).to.be.an('array');",
                  "if (res.length > 0 && res[0].id) { pm.environment.set('cliente_id', res[0].id); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "✅ 200 - Lista",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer <access_token>" }
                ]
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
              ],
              "body": "[\n  {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"nome\": \"Maria Silva\",\n    \"email\": \"maria@email.com\",\n    \"telefone\": \"11999990000\",\n    \"cpf_cnpj\": \"123.456.789-00\",\n    \"observacoes\": \"Cliente desde 2024\",\n    \"criado_em\": \"2026-02-07T18:00:00Z\",\n    \"atualizado_em\": \"2026-02-07T18:00:00Z\"\n  }\n]"
            }
          ]
        },
